"NumPy scalar types.  The classes can be used in ``isinstance`` checks and "
"can also be instantiated or used directly.  Direct use of these classes is "
"not typical, since their scalar counterparts (e.g. ``np.float64``) or "
"strings like ``\"float64\"`` can be used."
